Detailed Description

template<typename InternalCharType__, typename SizeType__>
class fsdict::Cell< TT_STANDARD, InternalCharType__, SizeType__ >

In this implementation, the member type_ encodes the function of the cell: 0: free cell 1: transition cell 2: state cell 3: final state cell.
